          title: "6. Cookies & Tracking",
          content: "We use two categories of cookies: (a) Essential cookies — login session, error logs, security; cannot be disabled; (b) Analytics cookies — page visit tracking, dwell time, location; only enabled with your consent. You may withdraw consent any time by clearing this site's data in your browser; the consent banner will reappear on your next visit."
